  <brief_title>Second-line Irinotecan and Capecitabine Versus Irinotecan for Gemcitabine and Cisplatin Refractory Biliary Tract Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Second-line Irinotecan and Capecitabine Versus Irinotecan Alone in Advanced Biliary Tract Cancer Patients Progressed After First-line Gemcitabine and Cisplatin: A Randomized Controlled Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
