  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is designed to investigate the effect of second-line irinotecan and capecitabine
      versus irinotecan alone for gemcitabine and cisplatin refractory advanced biliary tract
      cancer patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
